				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Infinite charges??<BR>
Are you mad?<BR>
There's a pretty huge difference between that and <BR>
the spell clerics get at level 1. First off, the spell takes a bit of time to get off. Second, it only lasts 18secs or so. Thirdly, it has a 15 minute recharge time. Yes, that means it takes 15 minutes until you can cast it again (or after having memorized it).<BR>
<BR>
Certainly, the spell can save a clerics life, but only in certain circumstances. With infinite charges, however, you would never die. Ever.<BR>
<BR>
I'd buy the idol for several hundred plat without blinking, so it's certainly a better item than the sbh.
